### How to use

Simply specify the maximum size.

```ts
app.post(
  '/hello',
  bodyLimit({
    maxSize: 15 * Unit.b, // byte,
    onError: (c) => {
      return c.text('oveflow :(', 413)
    },
  }),
  (c) => {
    return c.text('pass :)')
  }
)
```

